{
    "manually_checked": false,
    "poem_title": "¡Amor!",
    "author": "Gaspar Núñez de Arce",
    "poem_alt_title": "¡Oh eterno amor, que, en tu inmortal carrera",
    "corpus": "disco2_1",
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": "1",
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": "1",
                    "line_text": "¡Oh eterno amor, que, en tu inmortal carrera",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "2",
                    "line_text": "das a los seres vida y movimiento,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+--+-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "3",
                    "line_text": "con que entusiasta admiración te siento,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+---+++-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "4",
                    "line_text": "aunque invisible, palpitar doquiera!",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+---+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "¡Oh eterno amor, que, en tu inmortal carrera\ndas a los seres vida y movimiento,\ncon que entusiasta admiración te siento,\naunque invisible, palpitar doquiera!"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": "2",
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": "5",
                    "line_text": "Esclava tuya la creación entera,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "6",
                    "line_text": "se estremece y anima con tu aliento,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+-+----+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "7",
                    "line_text": "y es tu grandeza tal, que el pensamiento",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+--+-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "8",
                    "line_text": "te proclamara Dios, si Dios no hubiera.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+--+-+-+++-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Esclava tuya la creación entera,\nse estremece y anima con tu aliento,\ny es tu grandeza tal, que el pensamiento\nte proclamara Dios, si Dios no hubiera."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": "3",
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": "9",
                    "line_text": "Los impalpables átomos combinas",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "10",
                    "line_text": "con tu soplo magnético y fecundo;",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "11",
                    "line_text": "tú creas, tú transformas, tú iluminas,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+++-+-+--+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Los impalpables átomos combinas\ncon tu soplo magnético y fecundo;\ntú creas, tú transformas, tú iluminas,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": "4",
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": "12",
                    "line_text": "y en el cielo infinito, en el profundo",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "13",
                    "line_text": "mar, en la tierra atónita dominas,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+--+-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "14",
                    "line_text": "Amor, eterno Amor, alma del mundo.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+-++--+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "y en el cielo infinito, en el profundo\nmar, en la tierra atónita dominas,\nAmor, eterno Amor, alma del mundo."
        }
    ]
}